the Loom. Sales last year were Dollars 625m.
Mr Murdoch and Mrs Linda Wachner, head of Warnaco, said they were looking at
further joint ventures in Europe, Mexico and Latin America. Mrs Wachner
said: 'We need to look at how successful we are in Asia before going
further.'
