FT  30 SEP 94 / Merged firm will join top 50
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Two mid-tier City accountancy firms, Wilson Green and Silver Altman, have
announced a merger.
The new firm will practice from October 1 as Wilson Silver Altman. It will
have 12 partners, 60 staff and a combined fee income to place it in the top
50 in the UK, according to the firm.
